claim.claim-text:
1. A dual serial port data acquisition interface assembly for characterizing a servo control circuit of a data storage device comprising: 
a printed circuit board; 
a personal computer peripheral component interconnect connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing data between a personal computer and the data storage device; 
a first serial port connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing communication and synchronization data between the data storage device and the personal computer; 
a second serial port connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing a performance data of the servo control circuit from the data storage device to the personal computer; 
a programmed universal asynchronous receiver/transmitter microchip supported by the printed circuit board and communicating with the first serial port connector for controlling an interface between the personal computer and the data storage device; and 
a serial-to-parallel converter supported by the print circuit board and communicating with the second serial port connector for converting the performance data of the servo control circuit from a serial communication data string to a parallel communication data string for analysis by the personal computer.

9. A servo control circuit performance measurement station for measuring an operating point of a servo control circuit of a data storage device comprising: 
a personal computer with a chassis for supporting assemblies of the servo control circuit performance measurement station; 
a motherboard with a personal computer peripheral component interconnect expansion slot attached to the chassis; 
a dual serial port data acquisition interface assembly for characterizing the servo control circuit of the data storage device, the dual serial port data acquisition interface assembly communicating with the personal computer through the peripheral component interconnect expansion slot; 
a synchronous serial port cable attached on a first end to the dual serial port data acquisition interface assembly and communicating on a distal end with the data storage device; and 
an asynchronous serial port cable attached on a first end to the dual serial port data acquisition interface assembly and communicating on a distal end with the data storage device.

12. The servo control circuit performance measurement station of claim 9 in which the dual serial port data acquisition interface assembly comprises: 
a printed circuit board; 
a personal computer peripheral component interconnect connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing data between a personal computer and the data storage device; 
a first serial port connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing communication and synchronization data between the data storage device and the personal computer; 
a second serial port connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing a performance data of the servo control circuit from the data storage device to the personal computer; 
a programmed universal asynchronous receiver/transmitter microchip supported by the printed circuit board and communicating with the first serial port connector for controlling an interface between the personal computer and the data storage device; and 
a serial-to-parallel converter supported by the print circuit board and communicating with the second serial port connector for converting the performance data of the servo control circuit from a serial communication data string to a parallel communication data string for analysis by the personal computer.

13. A data storage device comprising: 
a basedeck; 
a spindle motor assembly supported by the basedeck; 
a disc attached to the spindle motor assembly, the disc having an information track for data storage; 
an actuator assembly supported by the basedeck and having a read/write head rotationally positionable adjacent the recording surface, the read/write head comprising a read element for reading data from the information track and a write element offset from the read element for writing data to the information track; 
a printed circuit board assembly attached to the basedeck; and 
a servo control circuit supported by the printed circuit board assembly position-controlling the actuator assembly, the servo control circuit characterized by means for characterizing the servo control circuit of the data storage device.

14. The data storage device of claim 13 in which the means for characterizing the servo control circuit of the data storage device comprises: 
a printed circuit board; 
a personal computer peripheral component interconnect connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing data between a personal computer and the data storage device; 
a first serial port connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing communication and synchronization data between the data storage device and the personal computer; 
a second serial port connector supported by the printed circuit board for passing a performance data of the servo control circuit from the data storage device to the personal computer; 
a programmed universal asynchronous receiver/transmitter microchip supported by the printed circuit board and communicating with the first serial port connector for controlling an interface between the personal computer and the data storage device; and 
a serial-to-parallel converter supported by the printed circuit board and communicating with the second serial port connector for converting the performance data of the servo control circuit from a serial communication data string to a parallel communication data string for analysis by the personal computer.
